

Ongoing

 * no bug/typo is too minor to report
   - send bug reports to cclive@googlegroups.com

 * improve portability
   - cclive is being developed on FreeBSD and Debian (both i386)
   - send any feedback to cclive@googlegroups.com

 * add support for new hosts
   - see host.c to get started
   - send patches to cclive@googlegroups.com
